Enhanced lsp-tools plugin with full LSP server installation automation
## Summary
Incorporated LSP server setup guidance from the claude-code-lsps repository into the lsp-tools plugin, adding automated installation scripts with per-server user prompts for seamless LSP toolchain setup.

## Changes Made
- Created `lsp-server-registry.md` - comprehensive reference with verification commands, installation instructions for all platforms
- Created 12 bash installation scripts (`scripts/bash/install-{language}-lsp.sh`) for Unix/macOS
- Created 12 PowerShell installation scripts (`scripts/powershell/install-{language}-lsp.ps1`) for Windows
- Created prerequisite check scripts (`check-prerequisites.sh`, `check-prerequisites.ps1`)
- Created verification scripts (`verify-lsp-servers.sh`, `verify-lsp-servers.ps1`)
- Enhanced `/lsp-tools:lsp-setup` command with:
  - Full prerequisite verification
  - Per-server installation prompts with user approval
  - New flags: `--verify-only`, `--skip-install`, `--skip-hooks`, `--skip-claudemd`
  - Post-installation verification
- Updated SKILL.md with server installation section
- Bumped version to 0.3.0 with full changelog

## Related Files
- plugins/lsp-tools/skills/lsp-enable/references/lsp-server-registry.md (new)
- plugins/lsp-tools/scripts/bash/*.sh (14 new scripts)
- plugins/lsp-tools/scripts/powershell/*.ps1 (14 new scripts)
- plugins/lsp-tools/commands/lsp-setup.md (enhanced)
- plugins/lsp-tools/skills/lsp-enable/SKILL.md (updated)
- plugins/lsp-tools/.claude-plugin/plugin.json (v0.3.0)
- plugins/lsp-tools/CHANGELOG.md (updated)

